fields.name: ОП
fields.title: ОП
fields.text:
oh, do you know

what you want?

do you know how to get it now?
look around
everyone
is not an enemy
for you

just believe in dream
and don’t lose your chance

unlock your brain
and dance with us!

free your mind
and dance, dance!


stay young!

stay punk!

dreamer!

winner!

catch your

fire

and never let it go..

oh, yeah I know
when a sorrow
interlace like a needle under skin 

and you think
you’re sick
you have no staminas
to get up

but believe in dream
and don’t lose your chance

unlock your brain
and dance with us!

free your mind
and dance, dance!

I will fade with you
I will shine with you
I will sing with you
like a shocking blue

I will fight for you
I will fight with you
I will.. never let you go..
